name: Northern Lights #33
description: A mesmerizing aurora borealis scene featuring vibrant waves of green, blue, and purple lights dancing across a deep night sky. The celestial display is rendered with glowing, semi-transparent gradients that shimmer above a dark mountain silhouette. Small white stars of varying sizes dot the rich navy background, while subtle reflections of the colorful aurora ripple across what appears to be a still lake surface at the base of the mountains, creating a serene northern landscape.

attributes.value: Vector Art with Gradients and Glow
